{"tid":1467064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日都仲有啲曙光, 依加比你地班死蠢搞輸啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:58.000Z","uid":125079,"like":23,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"94368a5bb9222e37d95ff1afb7f46348106c9776","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:17.000Z","msg":"唔好屌住, 其實今晚係一個好好既經驗<br />\n<br />\n機場啲鬼已經多過曬之前咁多次集會遊行既鬼, <span style=\"color: red;\">而機場依加只係第二日,</span> 已經出現咁多謠言, 帶風向既說話, 證明林鄭真係好驚搞到機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">琴日係因為義士用自己身體同鮮血, 先換取到全港市民既憤怒, 然後一齊入黎塞爆咗機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依樣野我地係唔可以忘記, 亦都係暫時既<br />\n民意所在<br />\n<br />\n點解會講暫時, 因為好多人好驚普通市民會割蓆, 所以我地好多人一直提住不割, 因為和理非前日係出於情感而出黎, <span style=\"color: red;\">而機場係個可以保護每一個人既地方,</span> 好多人怕一啲對示威者衝擊既情況出現會令佢地改變立場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">要永遠記住, 黑警無恥既暴行, 同埋香港市民善良有良知既心, 先係我地可以贏既最大武器</span><br />\n<br />\n對於鬼, 我地要阻止, 但唔係主動捉, 我地係塞爆機場, 唔係捉鬼大會<br />\n<br />\n我唔想要再有下一次黑警暴行打殘示威者, 甚至殺死示威者用黎換取下一次既極大民憤<br />\n<br />\n林鄭唔敢主動郁機場, 所以佢用緊離間計, 去製造民意, 其實冷靜落黎, 未必要係機場做啲主動阻礙人既野, 未必要無限捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">亦都唔需要係咁提不割, 因為好多人心目中一早已經割唔到</span>"},{"pid":"d5bb3f86dccda355c18d1c0a2ca03f70fe4e9c18","tid":1467064,"uid":109820,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"差啲屌咗，屌你<br />\nbtw<br />\n【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"8d25ba6ee37fa8f9f2fe36f15b566a2f0789df57","tid":1467064,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac74b3d1030f149a412d814ab1fc3d7e6c213e22","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">星期六 全部人再一次入機場<br />\n<br />\n星期一出係因為極度憤怒 唔可以白白忘記<br />\n<br />\n星期六係因為更多既香港人可以再企出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同時, 我地要依幾日去商討下點落規矩, 同點樣處理鬼, 黑警, 同旅客出入境既問題<br />\n<br />\n唔可以再好似之前無數次咁白白浪費民意"},{"pid":"7153433f55a6f6026749b2b664f8cf7c989d70a7","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:58.000Z","msg":"推 呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622a39a5c6bd782a8612bc17b24150cb57384342","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:46.000Z","msg":"要記住點解我地會嬲到<br />\n<br />\n一日內召集10幾萬人入機場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb45afc92c378a04303a59ffb5eb9ff3c3e62c7","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:14.000Z","msg":"全世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f998e16a4e68d497c9f67ff1776b6ca22f16a4","tid":1467064,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9214561f38c25a4cf0585c66ac3b2a99c95a02","tid":1467064,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:35.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea15ae59a9271ea6b99756f0e215949b9d0381b5","tid":1467064,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:06.000Z","msg":"明白，我都嬲<br />\n但唔好再屌啦，諗計補鑊仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84a010147049a41ef0f1b1c1a6eb31959eb6e2c","tid":1467064,"uid":235277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:14.000Z","msg":"雨傘運動輸咗係咁捉鬼 失焦<br />\n辛辛苦苦過去咗嘅兩個月<br />\n傷嘅傷 被捕嘅被捕 失去嘅失去<br />\n唔好再講乜野鬼唔鬼啦<br />\n811 有鬼做示威者開始就知一直都有鬼<br />\n我地做好自己要做嘅野咪得囉<br />\n集中返五大訴求<br />\n818再次上街"},{"pid":"f2577aeacfc42655955f214ef936ad18880cba94","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:08.000Z","msg":"寧死不割 但要進步 <br />\n<br />\n要諗清楚點先贏到依一局棋 <br />\n<br />\n要點先唔會白白浪費前線流既血<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">離間計黎架 大家清醒啲</span></span>"},{"pid":"539b9b73f304e3f35a5ea4935def6c0f1fe2382c","tid":1467064,"uid":81300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2577aeacfc42655955f214ef936ad18880cba94","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:08.000Z","msg":"寧死不割 但要進步 <br />\n<br />\n要諗清楚點先贏到依一局棋 <br />\n<br />\n要點先唔會白白浪費前線流既血<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">離間計黎架 大家清醒啲</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:28.000Z","msg":"唔係死蠢唔係輸ok？"},{"pid":"cf85eb33fbca519a7e97848244ff49034b957f06","tid":1467064,"uid":50588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"你個topic好差，已負皮"},{"pid":"5b506d8f660ab09b91a59583cc8fd7624d0e290b","tid":1467064,"uid":27225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"林奠用緊離間計<br />\n推！"},{"pid":"b5618253e42bbbfb3e11231f99608aa7ee905348","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:20.000Z","msg":"由星期日晚既地獄 到星期一既塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n一日都冇 證明市民有幾憤怒<br />\n<br />\n要相信人有良知"},{"pid":"7a0ee81c71ca18e331b9adbe51c8800e8c4e485f","tid":1467064,"uid":144787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:09.000Z","msg":"點解係都要標題黨?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757f03db7e24ef02864355129027ebe94ae8f4e1","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b506d8f660ab09b91a59583cc8fd7624d0e290b","tid":1467064,"uid":27225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"林奠用緊離間計<br />\n推！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"係 無錯 <br />\n<br />\n由有勇武出現個一刻 佢已經玩緊離間計<br />\n<br />\n玩民心 玩民意戰 <br />\n<br />\n依場運動就算輸 都唔可以輸係我地自己手中"},{"pid":"3015b28470b745c1fb816de53dd2b677031e1bc7","tid":1467064,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:50.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"18cd5d408c43d6ada90e70608d78a8f06df82138","tid":1467064,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母標題黨<br />\n好多人唔撚睇內文，唔好咁出post啦<br />\n<br />\n講好成個運動唔割，點解唔可以講好機場唔勇武唔捉鬼？"},{"pid":"180cf3ae9187487f3abaf4285f8ab6e8e99e0100","tid":1467064,"uid":76993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾標題 唔該重開"},{"pid":"9503ef99ce47952ed6224ee6f8bbe6fefba71dcd","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a0ee81c71ca18e331b9adbe51c8800e8c4e485f","tid":1467064,"uid":144787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:09.000Z","msg":"點解係都要標題黨?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為你睇下我之前出既post <br />\n<br />\n標題正正經經根本冇人睇 <br />\n<br />\n個個係度呻 係度驚 <br />\n<br />\n正正中曬林鄭想要既局面 離間 分化"},{"pid":"dfd4e119f3cefd911666d29720bb72966d08f745","tid":1467064,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:26.000Z","msg":"咪再做博屌嘅標題黨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ea511e262c56085fe3784ed09b23f3db57f3ff","tid":1467064,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"180cf3ae9187487f3abaf4285f8ab6e8e99e0100","tid":1467064,"uid":76993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾標題 唔該重開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:27.000Z","msg":"重開就冇人㩒入黎睇啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66335c4dc5ecb57fac3ce1deac032e2c58e7f3ae","tid":1467064,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">帶頭綁記者既人無比人捉會唔會太奇怪？</span></span>"}]}